  "detailed_description": "Experience nostalgic moments of excitement and wonder in this classic medieval fairy tale as you fight your way through the enchanted levels of Pitchfork Kingdom!<br><br>At its core, this is a fast-paced, action-packed side scroller that is easy to pick up. Pitchfork Kingdom aims to bring feelings of joy and humor as it creates memorable moments in its fabled world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Six Unique and Exciting Levels</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/8a399f8f5ca25501abb5ab5d3afe0c71.poster.avif?t=1663952433\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/8a399f8f5ca25501abb5ab5d3afe0c71.webm?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/8a399f8f5ca25501abb5ab5d3afe0c71.mp4?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Through simple yet deep mechanics, you will fight your way across the countryside, bandit-infested forests, and the castle walls while on your adventure. All the experience you gain will be put to the test with every new boss and mob that you fight.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >By Sword or Bow</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/9b4029e1fa5c64a47ce4de558bf3e757.poster.avif?t=1663952433\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/9b4029e1fa5c64a47ce4de558bf3e757.webm?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/9b4029e1fa5c64a47ce4de558bf3e757.mp4?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Equipped with your sword and your bow, the fate of the Kingdom is in your unlikely hands.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lots of Traps and Obstacles</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/ee61102b554be7acfb899e627e0ff0aa.poster.avif?t=1663952433\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/ee61102b554be7acfb899e627e0ff0aa.webm?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/ee61102b554be7acfb899e627e0ff0aa.mp4?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bandits, knights, and a variety of traps and obstacles will attempt to stop you from completing your quest and achieving the happy ending.",
  "about_the_game": "Experience nostalgic moments of excitement and wonder in this classic medieval fairy tale as you fight your way through the enchanted levels of Pitchfork Kingdom!<br><br>At its core, this is a fast-paced, action-packed side scroller that is easy to pick up. Pitchfork Kingdom aims to bring feelings of joy and humor as it creates memorable moments in its fabled world.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Six Unique and Exciting Levels</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/8a399f8f5ca25501abb5ab5d3afe0c71.poster.avif?t=1663952433\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/8a399f8f5ca25501abb5ab5d3afe0c71.webm?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/8a399f8f5ca25501abb5ab5d3afe0c71.mp4?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Through simple yet deep mechanics, you will fight your way across the countryside, bandit-infested forests, and the castle walls while on your adventure. All the experience you gain will be put to the test with every new boss and mob that you fight.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >By Sword or Bow</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/9b4029e1fa5c64a47ce4de558bf3e757.poster.avif?t=1663952433\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/9b4029e1fa5c64a47ce4de558bf3e757.webm?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/9b4029e1fa5c64a47ce4de558bf3e757.mp4?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Equipped with your sword and your bow, the fate of the Kingdom is in your unlikely hands.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Lots of Traps and Obstacles</h2><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/ee61102b554be7acfb899e627e0ff0aa.poster.avif?t=1663952433\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/ee61102b554be7acfb899e627e0ff0aa.webm?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1943810/extras/ee61102b554be7acfb899e627e0ff0aa.mp4?t=1663952433\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Bandits, knights, and a variety of traps and obstacles will attempt to stop you from completing your quest and achieving the happy ending.",
